00:11:07.330 --> 00:11:09.420
Because the bubble
is superluminal,

00:11:09.420 --> 00:11:12.190
any light that we see
would trail the bubble just

00:11:12.190 --> 00:11:14.480
like the sound of
a supersonic jet.

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:16.220
Ahead of the bubble,
you'd see nothing

00:11:16.220 --> 00:11:19.970
unless it stopped, in which case
all the photons and particles

00:11:19.970 --> 00:11:23.310
that are captured on its journey
would blast you into oblivion.

00:11:23.310 --> 00:11:25.320
Now, a few of you took
issue with my statement

00:11:25.320 --> 00:11:27.490
that it's never aliens.

00:11:27.490 --> 00:11:31.840
And fair enough, it's never
aliens until it's aliens.

00:11:31.840 --> 00:11:34.860
The point of this philosophy
is that the alien hypothesis

00:11:34.860 --> 00:11:37.960
is a bad place to start
because you can explains almost

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:40.650
any weird natural phenomenon
as having been produced

00:11:40.650 --> 00:11:43.020
by a super intelligent,
extremely high tech

00:11:43.020 --> 00:11:46.190
civilization with
inscrutable motives.

00:11:46.190 --> 00:11:47.580
Really anything.

00:11:47.580 --> 00:11:49.820
It's a week hypothesis
until you've generally

00:11:49.820 --> 00:11:53.200
ruled out everything else or
you actually see the mother ship

00:11:53.200 --> 00:11:56.090
and take an unsuspiciously
blurry photo of it.

